{"tid":1264904,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"學術討論，究竟電燈上面粒嘢係咩嚟？","createTime":"2019-06-29T02:22:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T10:41:33.000Z","uid":146956,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"149a0eb647525ff5b479bb335223562b5b779741","tid":1264904,"uid":146956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:22:01.000Z","msg":"我發現觀塘有燈柱上面多左粒嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagizer.imageshack.com/img922/8257/lnd69O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagizer.imageshack.com%2Fimg922%2F8257%2Flnd69O.jpg&h=d5f4d606&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖為觀塘明智街電燈）<br />\n就咁睇會以為有傻佬擺罐汽水上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我行遠啲發現原來唔止一個<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagizer.imageshack.com/img924/4363/H70ymC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagizer.imageshack.com%2Fimg924%2F4363%2FH70ymC.jpg&h=64ee9e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連新建成嘅燈都有呢粒嘢（圖為康寧道燈柱）<br />\n新電燈就係之前話有cam 果隻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/281929/%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82-%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E5%8D%80%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1-%E8%A8%AD%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E6%A9%9F-%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F281929%2F%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582-%25E8%25A7%2580%25E5%25A1%2598%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%25A3%259D%25E6%2599%25BA%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2587%2588%25E6%259F%25B1-%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E7%259B%25A3%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%2594%259D%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E6%2594%25B6%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%2595%25B8%25E6%2593%259A&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6lKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=11262ba5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/281929/%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82-%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E5%8D%80%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D%E6%99%BA%E6%85%A7%E7%87%88%E6%9F%B1-%E8%A8%AD%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E6%A9%9F-%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A</a><br />\n我同朋友查過，見到有新聞係話係燈上面加訊號接收器黎check啲燈有無壞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/168619/生產力局創智能路燈-實時傳遞路燈情況\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F168619%2F%E7%94%9F%E7%94%A2%E5%8A%9B%E5%B1%80%E5%89%B5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E8%B7%AF%E7%87%88-%E5%AF%A6%E6%99%82%E5%82%B3%E9%81%9E%E8%B7%AF%E7%87%88%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6lKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=4fd5d9da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/168619/生產力局創智能路燈-實時傳遞路燈情況</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180316/57950564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180316%2F57950564&d=Ns8Dgi7AEu9liZcLsKty6lKEWDR5zjN73Co06CeqttY%3D&h=bebf0112\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180316%2F57950564&h=ba164e5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180316/57950564</a><br />\n但暫時淨係會新蒲崗同啟德新發展區測試，未有計劃推廣至全港<br />\n<br />\n同埋觀塘有啲電燈頂未有呢舊嘢，例如係裕民坊果啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagizer.imageshack.com/img921/22/i2QPP8.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagizer.imageshack.com%2Fimg921%2F22%2Fi2QPP8.jpg%20&h=b265955c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imagizer.imageshack.com/img924/3449/ImZ6mZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagizer.imageshack.com%2Fimg924%2F3449%2FImZ6mZ.jpg&h=f0196368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n究竟果粒喺咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9d96cfe3479dad3fd151e559e809adef3c4f767","tid":1264904,"uid":186844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:23:41.000Z","ms